WEBVTT

00:07.002 --> 00:11.574
Welcome to the grand
re-opening of wiztech.

00:15.875 --> 00:20.213
We owe a big debt of gratitude to
justin russo for saving wiztech

00:20.248 --> 00:24.551
By removing the plastic balls
from our hallowed halls.

00:24.585 --> 00:27.689
And we know how dangerous
plastic is to wizards.

00:27.723 --> 00:31.194
we hate plastic! We hate plastic!

00:31.228 --> 00:35.199
Thank you, thank you. We're wizards.
We all hate plastic, right?

00:37.437 --> 00:41.708
Saving wiztech wouldn't have been possible
without the generous financial support

00:41.743 --> 00:44.878
Of the wizworld industries,
so let's...

00:48.649 --> 00:50.851
I, uh, hope that's ok
with you, professor.

00:50.885 --> 00:54.388
Of course. A few advertisements
is a small price to pay

00:54.422 --> 00:57.725
For the reopening of
our beloved school.

00:57.759 --> 01:00.828
As long as the sign
isn't made of plastic.

01:00.862 --> 01:02.463
Ahh.

01:02.497 --> 01:05.600
Now, I would like to invite
wiztech student, hugh normous,

01:05.634 --> 01:07.502
To cut the ceremonial ribbon.

01:14.677 --> 01:18.915
Oh, no thanks. My giant hands
will never fit in those scissors.

01:18.949 --> 01:21.084
I'll have to use my own.

01:27.758 --> 01:31.961
- Gee...
- Oh, are you kidding me?

01:33.000 --> 01:39.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:42.073 --> 01:44.174
Whoa. Finally.

01:44.209 --> 01:46.376
Tv how I want it.

01:46.410 --> 01:48.244
All commercials.

01:50.647 --> 01:53.015
Thanks for coming
back with me, alex.

01:53.249 --> 01:56.752
And I promise I'll make you forget about
that boyfriend who broke your heart.

01:58.188 --> 01:59.421
Yeah.

01:59.456 --> 02:00.622
Dean.

02:00.657 --> 02:02.524
Almost forgot about him.

02:02.558 --> 02:05.360
Thanks for hitting the
reset button on that.

02:05.395 --> 02:06.928
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

02:06.963 --> 02:09.698
No, this is a new start for you.

02:09.732 --> 02:12.100
You have no idea
what's possible here.

02:12.135 --> 02:14.336
And you're a very special girl.

02:15.838 --> 02:19.140
very, very special.

02:22.077 --> 02:24.846
More special than
you will ever know!

02:24.880 --> 02:28.750
Um, I'm sorry. I can't hear you
with all this evil thunder.

02:28.784 --> 02:31.285
- Oh. I said you're special.
- Oh, thank you.

02:33.055 --> 02:36.390
ominous thunder and
lightning brought to you by

02:36.425 --> 02:38.225
The wizworld weather channel.

02:39.695 --> 02:41.295
Now, that could get annoying.

02:41.496 --> 02:44.799
You think this would look
good with my board shorts?

02:44.833 --> 02:47.834
- I'm gonna get it anyway.
- Ok. You do that.

02:49.536 --> 02:51.738
* well, you know everything's
gonna be a breeze *

02:51.772 --> 02:53.806
* that the end will no
doubt justify the means *

02:54.074 --> 02:55.742
* you can fix any problem
at the slightest ease *

02:55.776 --> 02:57.476
* yes, please *

02:57.511 --> 02:59.378
* well, you might find out
it'll go to your head *

03:00.046 --> 03:01.814
* when you write a report
on a book you never read *

03:01.848 --> 03:04.349
* with a snap of your fingers
you can make your bed *

03:04.383 --> 03:06.084
* that's what I said *

03:06.118 --> 03:09.054
* everything is not what it seems *

03:09.088 --> 03:12.825
* when you can get all you
wanted in your wildest dreams *

03:12.859 --> 03:16.662
* you might run into trouble
if you go to extremes *

